trans-unit.source: Represents the security settings for the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding" />.
trans-unit.target: Representa la configuración de seguridad para <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding> class is designed for interoperation with services that implement WS-* specifications.
trans-unit.target: La clase <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding> está diseñada para la interoperación con servicios que implementan las especificaciones de WS-*.

trans-unit.source: The transport security for this binding is Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) over HTTP, or HTTPS.
trans-unit.target: La seguridad de transporte para este enlace es Capa de sockets seguros (SSL) sobre HTTP o HTTPS.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the message-level security settings for this binding.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la configuración de seguridad del nivel del mensaje para este enlace.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.NonDualMessageSecurityOverHttp" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Instancia de <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.NonDualMessageSecurityOverHttp" />.

trans-unit.source: The default value includes: <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.NonDualMessageSecurityOverHttp.EstablishSecurityContext" /> with default set to <see langword="true" />, <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.MessageSecurityOverHttp.ClientCredentialType" /> is <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.MessageCredentialType.Windows" />, <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.MessageSecurityOverHttp.AlgorithmSuite" /> is <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityAlgorithmSuite.Basic256" />, and <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.MessageSecurityOverHttp.NegotiateServiceCredential" /> is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado incluye: <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.NonDualMessageSecurityOverHttp.EstablishSecurityContext" /> con el valor predeterminado definido en <see langword="true" />, <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.MessageSecurityOverHttp.ClientCredentialType" /> es <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.MessageCredentialType.Windows" />, <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.MessageSecurityOverHttp.AlgorithmSuite" /> es <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityAlgorithmSuite.Basic256" /> y <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.MessageSecurityOverHttp.NegotiateServiceCredential" /> es <see langword="true" />.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the message <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.SecurityMode" /> for this binding.
trans-unit.target: Especifica el <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.SecurityMode" /> del mensaje para este enlace.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.SecurityMode" /> for this binding.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.SecurityMode" /> para este enlace.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.SecurityMode.Message" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado es <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.SecurityMode.Message" />.

trans-unit.source: This property determines whether the settings from the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpSecurity.Transport%2A> and/or <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpSecurity.Message%2A> property buckets may or may not become effective.
trans-unit.target: Esta propiedad determina si la configuración de los depósitos de seguridad <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpSecurity.Transport%2A> y/o <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpSecurity.Message%2A> puede o no volverse efectiva.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that contains the transport-level security settings for this binding.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un objeto que contiene los valores de seguridad de nivel de transporte para este enlace.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity" /> for this binding.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity" /> para este enlace.

trans-unit.source: The default value includes a <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity.ClientCredentialType" /> of <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.HttpClientCredentialType.None" /> and a <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity.ProxyCredentialType" /> of <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.HttpProxyCredentialType.None" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado incluye <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity.ClientCredentialType" /> de <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.HttpClientCredentialType.None" /> y <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity.ProxyCredentialType" /> de <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.HttpProxyCredentialType.None" />.

trans-unit.source: You can use the object returned by this property to set the transport security settings for the binding.
trans-unit.target: Puede utilizar el objeto devuelto por esta propiedad para establecer la configuración de seguridad del transporte para el enlace.
